node.text:
I'm just tryna match your words with your actions
I need more than satisfaction
Rain on roof outside window , gray light, deep covers and warm blankets. Rain and nip of autumn in air, nostalgia.
Tú sabes cómo lo hacemo', baby
non c’è stupore, né paura, ma la sola consapevolezza di vivere una sensazione inevitabile, necessaria
There’s a battle between what we feel and what we know

Damn baby all I need is a lil' bit
A lil' bit of this, a lil' bit of that
Gioca col fuoco o muori di freddo
Un mondo in bianco e nero
Aveva il suono di una melodia lontana!
E non c’è bisogno di niente! 🌞

Darling, darling, oh, turn the lights back on now.
Watching, watching, as the credits all roll down.
